A new kind of heartbeat application is needed

Current heartbeat implications only ensure communication is established.  These are usually built simply in a 2d fashion with no depth beyond the generally knowledge that applications can "talk" to one another.  As technology grows beyond known boundaries, both intentional and unintentional technical issues are more frequently experienced.

Similar to the lesser known qualities of the human heart, this would allow further dimensions of utilization for developers to work with.  

